The Richmond Times-Dispatch is the primary daily newspaper in Richmond, the capital of Virginia, United States, as well as the Virginia cities of Petersburg, Chester. Hopewell, Colonial Heights, Charlottesville, Lynchburg, Waynesboro, and is also a default paper for rural regions of the state. The RTD has published in some form for more than 150 years.
